---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Design System"
  description="Design tokens, components, and patterns for ekel.dev"
  url="https://ekel.dev/design-system"
>
  <div class="w-full max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <header class="mb-12">
      <h1 class="mt-8 mb-4 text-3xl sm:text-4xl tracking-tighter font-medium text-foreground leading-tight">Design System</h1>
      <p class="text-base text-muted-foreground leading-7">
        Design tokens, component patterns, and usage guidelines for ekel.dev.
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- Colors -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight text-foreground">Colors</h2>
      <p class="mb-6 text-sm text-muted-foreground">Semantic color tokens via CSS custom properties. Swatches show <code>token</code> followed by the light-mode oklch value.</p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="rounded-none border border-border/40 bg-transparent p-6">
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Background &mdash; bg-background</p>
          <div class="w-full h-10 rounded-none border border-border/40 bg-background mb-2"></div>
          <code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">oklch(0.97 0 0) / dark: oklch(0.175 0 0)</code>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-none border border-border/40 bg-transparent p-6">
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Foreground &mdash; text-foreground</p>
          <div class="w-full h-10 rounded-none border border-border/40 bg-foreground mb-2"></div>
          <code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">oklch(0.175 0 0) / dark: oklch(0.97 0 0)</code>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-none border border-border/40 bg-transparent p-6">
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Card &mdash; bg-card</p>
          <div class="w-full h-10 rounded-none border border-border/40 bg-card mb-2"></div>
          <code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">oklch(1 0 0) / dark: oklch(0.205 0 0)</code>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-none border border-border/40 bg-transparent p-6">
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Muted &mdash; bg-muted</p>
          <div class="w-full h-10 rounded-none border border-border/40 bg-muted mb-2"></div>
          <code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">oklch(0.96 0 0) / dark: oklch(0.269 0 0)</code>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-none border border-border/40 bg-transparent p-6">
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Muted Foreground &mdash; text-muted-foreground</p>
          <div class="w-full h-10 rounded-none border border-border/40 bg-muted-foreground mb-2"></div>
          <code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">oklch(0.45 0 0) / dark: oklch(0.708 0 0)</code>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-none border border-border/40 bg-transparent p-6">
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Border &mdash; border-border</p>
          <div class="w-full h-10 rounded-none border-2 border-border mb-2"></div>
          <code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">oklch(0 0 0 / 10%) / dark: oklch(1 0 0 / 10%)</code>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Typography -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight text-foreground">Typography</h2>
      <p class="mb-6 text-sm text-muted-foreground">Geist Sans for body and headings. Geist Mono for code. Noto Naskh Arabic for arabic text.</p>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">Page heading (h1)</p>
          <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl tracking-tighter font-medium text-foreground mb-1">The quick brown fox</h1>
          <code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">text-3xl sm:text-4xl tracking-tighter font-medium text-foreground</code>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">Section heading (h2)</p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl tracking-tight font-medium text-foreground mb-1">The quick brown fox</h2>
          <code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">text-2xl sm:text-3xl tracking-tight font-medium text-foreground</code>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">Card title (h3)</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium tracking-tight text-foreground mb-1">The quick brown fox</h3>
          <code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">text-xl font-medium tracking-tight text-foreground</code>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">Body text</p>
          <p class="text-base leading-7 text-foreground mb-1">The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog. Geist Sans renders cleanly at all sizes with generous line height for readability.</p>
          <code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">text-base leading-7 text-foreground</code>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">Secondary text</p>
          <p class="text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground mb-1">Descriptions, metadata, and supporting content use muted foreground.</p>
          <code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground</code>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">Monospace / code</p>
          <code class="text-sm text-foreground bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5">const x = 42;</code>
          <p class="mt-2"><code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">font-mono text-sm</code></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8">
        <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Available font tokens</p>
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-border/40">
              <th class="text-left py-2 font-medium text-foreground">Token</th>
              <th class="text-left py-2 font-medium text-foreground">CSS Variable</th>
              <th class="text-left py-2 font-medium text-foreground">Font Stack</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr class="border-b border-border/20">
              <td class="py-2 text-foreground">font-sans</td>
              <td class="py-2"><code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">var(--font-sans)</code></td>
              <td class="py-2 text-muted-foreground">Geist Sans, sans-serif</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-border/20">
              <td class="py-2 text-foreground">font-mono</td>
              <td class="py-2"><code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">var(--font-mono)</code></td>
              <td class="py-2 text-muted-foreground">Geist Mono, monospace</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Spacing -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight text-foreground">Spacing</h2>

      <table class="w-full text-sm">
        <thead>
          <tr class="border-b border-border/40">
            <th class="text-left py-2 font-medium text-foreground">Usage</th>
            <th class="text-left py-2 font-medium text-foreground">Mobile</th>
            <th class="text-left py-2 font-medium text-foreground">Desktop</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr class="border-b border-border/20">
            <td class="py-2 text-foreground">Page header bottom margin</td>
            <td class="py-2 text-muted-foreground"><code>mb-10</code></td>
            <td class="py-2 text-muted-foreground"><code>sm:mb-16</code></td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-border/20">
            <td class="py-2 text-foreground">Section gap</td>
            <td class="py-2 text-muted-foreground"><code>mt-16</code></td>
            <td class="py-2 text-muted-foreground"><code>sm:mt-24</code></td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-border/20">
            <td class="py-2 text-foreground">Section heading margin</td>
            <td class="py-2 text-muted-foreground"><code>mb-6</code></td>
            <td class="py-2 text-muted-foreground"><code>sm:mb-8</code></td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-border/20">
            <td class="py-2 text-foreground">Container top padding</td>
            <td class="py-2 text-muted-foreground"><code>pt-24</code></td>
            <td class="py-2 text-muted-foreground"><code>pt-24</code></td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-border/20">
            <td class="py-2 text-foreground">Card internal padding</td>
            <td class="py-2 text-muted-foreground"><code>p-5</code></td>
            <td class="py-2 text-muted-foreground"><code>p-8</code></td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-border/20">
            <td class="py-2 text-foreground">Grid gap</td>
            <td class="py-2 text-muted-foreground"><code>gap-6</code></td>
            <td class="py-2 text-muted-foreground"><code>gap-6</code></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <!-- Borders & Radii -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight text-foreground">Borders &amp; Radii</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">
        <div class="rounded-none border border-border/40 bg-transparent p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide">All Sharp</p>
          <p class="text-foreground font-medium">rounded-none</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-sm border border-border/40 bg-transparent p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide">Small</p>
          <p class="text-foreground font-medium">rounded-sm</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-md border border-border/40 bg-transparent p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide">Medium</p>
          <p class="text-foreground font-medium">rounded-md</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">Default border</p>
          <div class="w-full h-12 border border-border/40 flex items-center justify-center bg-transparent">
            <code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">border border-border/40</code>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">Hover border</p>
          <div class="w-full h-12 border border-border/80 flex items-center justify-center bg-transparent">
            <code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">hover:border-border/80</code>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Layout -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight text-foreground">Layout</h2>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-sm">
        <div class="rounded-none border border-border/40 bg-transparent p-6">
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">Container</p>
          <code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8 pt-24</code>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-2">All pages use the same container shell from Layout.astro.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-none border border-border/40 bg-transparent p-6">
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">Content width constraint</p>
          <code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">max-w-3xl mx-auto</code>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-2">Detail pages (notes, works) constrain content for readability.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-none border border-border/40 bg-transparent p-6">
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">Card grid</p>
          <code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6</code>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-2">Works and notes listing pages.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Navbar -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight text-foreground">Navbar</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4">Fixed top bar with text links. Desktop: horizontal links + theme toggle. Mobile: bottom sheet with icons + labels.</p>

      <div class="rounded-none border border-border/40 bg-transparent p-6">
        <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">Desktop nav links</p>
        <code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">text-sm font-medium no-underline transition-colors</code>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-2">Active: <code>text-foreground</code>. Inactive: <code>text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground</code>.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Cards -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight text-foreground">Cards</h2>

      <div class="rounded-none border border-border/40 bg-transparent p-8 mb-4">
        <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">Standard card</p>
        <code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">rounded-none border border-border/40 bg-transparent p-8 hover:border-border/80</code>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-2">Used for note and work cards. Flat, no shadow, subtle border that darkens on hover.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Page Structure -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight text-foreground">Page Structure</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4">Every page follows this pattern:</p>
      <pre class="bg-muted text-sm text-foreground p-6 rounded-none border border-border/40 overflow-x-auto leading-relaxed">{`<Layout title="..." description="...">
  <div class="w-full ...">
    <section class="mb-10 sm:mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl tracking-tighter font-medium text-foreground">
        Page Title
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-muted-foreground">
        Description
      </p>
    </section>
    <!-- Content sections with mt-16 sm:mt-24 -->
  </div>
</Layout>`}</pre>
    </section>

    <!-- Links -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight text-foreground">Links</h2>

      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div>
          <a href="#" class="text-foreground underline decoration-border/30 underline-offset-2 hover:text-muted-foreground transition-colors">Internal link</a>
          <p class="mt-1"><code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">underline decoration-border/30 underline-offset-2 font-medium</code></p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">External link with icon</a>
          <p class="mt-1"><code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Auto-adds arrow via a[target="_blank"]::after</code></p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <a href="#" class="text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors">Tag link</a>
          <p class="mt-1"><code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground</code></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Grid Background -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight text-foreground">Grid Background</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4">Ampcode-style column grid overlay visible on desktop only. Dashed vertical lines at 25%, 50%, and 75% positions.</p>

      <div class="rounded-none border border-border/40 bg-transparent p-6">
        <code class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">0.5px border-dashed border-border/30 via CSS position overlay</code>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-2">Hidden on mobile (<code>hidden md:block</code>). Fixed positioning, pointer-events-none.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="mb-16">
      <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
        This page documents the design tokens used on <a href="/" class="text-foreground">ekel.dev</a>.
        Built with Astro, Svelte, Tailwind CSS 4, and shadcn-svelte.
      </p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</Layout>
